demonstration plugin for the graph-based segmentation algorithm described by
Felzenszwalb and Huttenlocher in:

Efficient Graph-Based Image Segmentation.
Pedro F. Felzenszwalb and Daniel P. Huttenlocher.
International Journal of Computer Vision, Volume 59, Number 2, September 2004.

http://people.cs.uchicago.edu/~pff/segment/

The original segmentation source code is licensed under the GPL.  It has been
slightly modified for the plugin.  Changes from the original source code are
detailed in the file diff-from-orig.txt
